- Flex is a style component to position sub-elements in one dimension without relying on external CSS

### Basic usage of Flex
```jsx
<Flex onClick={function noRefCheck(){}}>
  <Button>
    Primary
  </Button>
  <Button kind="tertiary">
    Tertiary
  </Button>
  <Button kind="tertiary">
    Tertiary
  </Button>
</Flex>
```

### Import

```js
import { Flex } from "@vibe/core";
```